# Full E1 pytest roster: project root README.md Tests / E1 mapping; spec-phase2.md §14 Honesty vs CI (same pointers as ci.yml, dependabot.yml).
# Optional RAG: docs/rag/le-vibe-phase2-chunks.md (spec-phase2 §14 table; not pytest) — SECURITY Related docs; packaging/scripts/ci-smoke.sh + .github/workflows/ci.yml headers.
